::Razor::

Razor drops soem tools after two days of nonstop work.

&quot;Finally base is set up. Computer, close blast doors and activate defense systems.&quot;

Computer: Processing request...

The big metal blast door shut over the cave entrance as deflector shields and auto guns come online.

Computer: Request finished.

&quot;It&#39;s a good thing I planned for all this,&quot; says Razor. &quot;Now to bring in some friends and put my plan into order.&quot;

Razor activates a comm system in the main computer room.
His first transmission is aimed at Cybertron, but is incoded so only those intended will recieve it.

&quot;Deemos, Arrow, if you recieve this then you know that I live. I made it to Pre-Historic Earth as planned. It&#39;s time to raise our army. Follow my signal here and join me. I hope to see you soon. Your friend, Razor.&quot;

Razor then switches so the next transmission is broadcasted all over Earth. However it is also incoded and only a few bots really have a chance of decoding it.

&quot;Hello Cybertronian, and maybe non Cybertronian, Transformers. I am Razor. Do you wish to over come the foolish factions on this world, and reign supreme? Join me, and help build a new faction. We will rule in the new order! Follow this signal to my base to join. Over and out.&quot;

The messages are sent out, and Razor waits.

OOC: I&#39;ve already talked to the people who will recieve the messages, they know who they are, and they should be the only ones to respond.

**********************************************************************

A new order is coming to NBW, are you ready?


--Boundary_(ID_YgDDlm2m2Uzc+ictiP9k8g)
